queries.name: SelectUsersCount
queries.raw:
SELECT COUNT(`id`)  AS `users_count`
FROM `users`
WHERE `id` IN (?)

queries.name: SelectUsersUnion
queries.raw:
SELECT `id` FROM `users` WHERE `id` IN (?)
UNION (SELECT `id` FROM `users` WHERE `id` IN (?))

queries.name: SelectUsersUnionInParens
queries.raw:
SELECT `id` FROM `users` WHERE `id` IN (?)
UNION (SELECT `id` FROM `users` WHERE `id` IN (?))

queries.name: GetQueryIDByID
queries.raw:
SELECT query.`id`
FROM query
WHERE query.`id` = ?
